4. If (Weight is Slim), then (Quality is Low) (1)
5. If (Length is Short), then (Quality is Low) (1)
6. If (Diameter is Large) and (Length is Long) and (Weight is Heavy), then (Quality is High) (1)
7. If (Width is Small) and (Weight is Slim), then (Quality is Low) (1)
8. If (Diameter is Large) and (Length is Short), then (Quality is Middle) (1)
9. If (Width is Large) and (Weight is Heavy), then (Quality is High) (1)
10. If (Diameter is Small) and (Weight is Slim), then (Quality is Low) (1)
11. If (Length is Long) and (Weight is Middle), then (Quality is Middle-High) (1)
12. If (Length is Middle) and (Weight is Heavy), then (Quality is Middle-High) (1)
13. If (Width is Small) and (Length is Long), then (Quality is Middle) (1)
14. If (Diameter is Small) and (Length is Long), then (Quality is Middle) (1)
